org.sql: SELECT wiki_pages.*, wiki_contents.updated_at FROM wiki_pages LEFT JOIN wiki_contents ON wiki_contents.page_id = wiki_pages.id WHERE wiki_pages.wiki_id = "$1" ORDER BY title

rewrites.sql: SELECT wiki_pages.*, wiki_contents.updated_at FROM wiki_pages LEFT JOIN wiki_contents ON wiki_contents.page_id = wiki_pages.id WHERE wiki_pages.wiki_id = "$1" ORDER BY title LIMIT 1
